lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I thought we had 
something special, 
but then you walked away 
A simple mistake, 
a little toot that ruined our perfect day
I never meant to let it slip, 
it was just a harmless sound
But now you're gone 
and I'm left standing 
on shaky ground

[Chorus]
Why did you leave me 
for one tiny fart?
Was our love so fragile, 
torn apart?
I'm lost and confused, 
unsure of what went wrong
Will I ever find 
where I truly belong?
[Verse 2]
I can't help but wonder 
if it was all just an excuse
To break free from the ties that bind us, 
no longer feeling amused
Did my accidental slip-up 
really cause such disdain?
Or were there deeper issues 
lurking beneath the surface pain?
